BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:O-Y--JzdCSYm9NKdg3VPS
SUMMARY:Spring Beer Fest
DTSTAMP:20260407T043746Z
DTSTART:20250509T230100Z
DESCRIPTION:This mini beer festival celebrates our new spring seasonal rele
	ases\, as well as a kind of retrospective on some of our favorite releases
	 of the last couple of months. All rounded out with some great guest taps 
	from a bunch of great local producers and friends.Our Spring Beer Fest wil
	l include 12 cask ales\, including our Spring seasonal favorite Stinging N
	ettle Ale and a new version of an old Machine House classic\, Oyster Stout
	. We will also have casks of our collaboration beers with Fast Fashion\, G
	reyscale Brewing and Lowercase (the last ever cask of London Pilsner!).Plu
	s several excellent guest beers from Structures Brewing\, Human People\, E
	9\, Bizarre Brewing\, and ciders from Alpenfire\, Woodinville and Yonder t
	o round out our selection.Come on by throughout the weekend to sample thro
	ugh everything.Spring Beer Fest is May 9-11 at Machine House in Hillman Ci
	ty. Perfect timing for Seattle Beer Week\, and Mothers Day! This event is 
	free to enter and open to all ages.\n\nFrom Seattle Beer Week
LOCATION:Location ID: mabn0quq
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:beer-week
CATEGORIES:Seattle Beer Week
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT5H29M
END:VEVENT
